						<summary>

						<p>On a hero-stone set up in the Hanumantadēva temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 13th century.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to Mallaya-nāyaka by the eight <hi rend="italic">Hiṭṭus</hi> and five <hi rend="italic">maṭhas.</hi> It mentions Sesuvinahaḷḷi. The record is damaged.</p>						

						</summary>
